<p>As a C++ programmer coming to the C# world, while writing multi-thread programs, the thing I miss the most is <a href="https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/thread/condition_variable">condition variable</a>.</p>

<p>I googled for a while trying to find a built-in counterpart or a crafted solution in .NET Framework. I failed. The top results returned were either wrong statements, or a design that lacked generalization.</p>

